TTS App is a powerful text-to-speech mobile application that supports both on-device (free) and premium cloud voices.

Features:
- Read text from PDF and TXT files.
- Multiple high-quality voices and languages.
- Offline support using on-device TTS engines.
- Audio export (MP3/WAV) to share with others.
- Dark mode and customizable settings.
- Transparent pricing for cloud TTS providers (Amazon Polly, Google Cloud, Azure).

Perfect for students, commuters, and anyone who prefers listening over reading!
